code: @Test public void cookieProcessorIsCustomized() {     ServletWebServerApplicationContext applicationContext = (ServletWebServerApplicationContext) new SpringApplication(TestConfiguration.class, LegacyCookieProcessorConfiguration.class).run().     Context context = (Context) ((TomcatWebServer) applicationContext.getWebServer()).getTomcat().getHost().findChildren()[0].     assertThat(context.getCookieProcessor()).isInstanceOf(LegacyCookieProcessor.class). }
